reviewText: I suggest you get the whole set. I have used these for years going back to the VHS tapes. I still use all of them. Sometimes 101 AM 201 PM or 201 & 301. 401 & 501 are serious workouts, but even if I can't get all the way through them it is okay. I am 63 and Dr. Chen's programs have been a blessing to my health and well being.
